    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-11-09T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-11-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="156"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d156">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Sill</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Seoul</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-11-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 9, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The King is still in grievous peril and under duress of conspirators. The
                    representatives of England, Russia, France, and myself are urging Japanese to
                    protect the King and restore status by necessary temporary force.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Sill.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
